title: Fan Music - Warwick vs Annie and Amumu

embed.description: Something I did for fun out of samples from League of Legends. This is a non commercial project, all rights remain with Riot inc.

body:
I found a bunch of samples from LOL and decided to make a little song story out of them. I thought some of you may enjoy it.

Warwick is feeling hungry and heads out to find some food. He runs across Annie and Amumu playing in the Jungle and goes in for the gank....

You can find the sound file in the link

replies.body:
I like how you connect their quotes together.
"Play time! Come play with me"
